## ğŸ® Commands
- `gitgotchi status` - See your companion
- `gitgotchi pet` - Give them affection
- `gitgotchi story` - Hear a code story
- `gitgotchi evolve` - Check evolution progress
- `gitgotchi name <name>` - Give your companion a name

